 	<!--<div class="disclosure disclosure-top">This post may contain affiliate links.</div>-->
		
	<div class="post-content">
		<span id="dpsp-post-content-markup" data-image-pin-it="false"></span>
<p><em>This rustic blueberry galette is the perfect summer dessert, especially for the 4th of July! Juicy, sweet blueberries are wrapped in a golden, flaky, butter crust that’s easier to make than a traditional pie. With just a few simple pantry ingredients and minimal prep, this galette comes together quickly and bakes into a show stopping treat. Serve it warm with whipped cream or vanilla ice cream for the ultimate crowd pleaser.</em></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="1803" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-1200x1803.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47473" style="width:775px;height:auto" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-500x751.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-1022x1536.jpg 1022w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></figure>



<p>This blueberry galette has become a summer staple for my family, especially around the Fourth of July when fresh berries are at their peak. After testing this recipe countless times over the years, I’ve refined the technique to be simple enough for beginners while still delivering that perfectly flaky crust. I always emphasize using very cold butter and ice water to guarantee a tender crust. Seriously, it has to be COLD! these small details truly make a difference. Whether you&#8217;re baking for guests or just treating yourself, this is a dessert you can count on to impress.</p>



<p>I can make this with my eyes closed now, and with my easy instructions, I know you&#8217;ll be able to also! Enjoy, and I hope this becomes a family tradition for you like it has for us.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group has-lightblue-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-why-you-ll-love-this-blueberry-galette"><strong>Why You’ll Love This Blueberry Galette</strong></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Easier than a full pie</li>



<li>Juicy, sweet blueberries with a zingy lemon twist</li>



<li>Buttery, golden, crisp crust</li>



<li>No pie pan needed. Just parchment paper and a baking sheet</li>



<li>Beautifully rustic and perfect for summer gatherings</li>
</ul>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Blueberry Galette Ingredients: blueberries, Cornstarch, coarse sugar, butter, all purpose flour, lemon zest, salt, granulated sugar, egg, water" class="wp-image-47474" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1200x799.jpg" alt="Blueberry Galette Ingredients: blueberries, Cornstarch, coarse sugar, butter, all purpose flour, lemon zest, salt, granulated sugar, egg, water" class="wp-image-47474" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-Ingredients.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>Ingredients You’ll Need</strong></h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Dough:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>1 ¼ cup all-purpose flour</li>



<li>2 tablespoons granulated sugar</li>



<li>¼ teaspoon salt <em>(add ¼ tsp more if using unsalted butter)</em></li>



<li>8 tablespoons cold salted butter, cut into tablespoons</li>



<li>2 ½ to 3 ½ tablespoons ice cold water</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">For the Blueberry Filling:</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>4 cups blueberries</li>



<li>1/3 cup granulated sugar</li>



<li>2 tablespoons lemon juice</li>



<li>2 teaspoons lemon zest <em>(or lime zest for variation)</em></li>



<li>2 tablespoons cornstarch</li>
</ul>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-egg-wash-topping">Egg Wash Topping</h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>1 egg</li>



<li>2 tablespoons water</li>



<li>Coarse sugar for sprinkling (optional)</li>
</ul>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading"><strong>How to Make a Blueberry Galette</strong></h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-make-the-dough"><strong>Make the Dough</strong></h3>



<p>In a food processor, pulse together flour, sugar, and salt. Add the cold butter and pulse until pea-sized. Add ice water a tablespoon at a time, pulsing until it just begins to clump. Test by squeezing a handful, if it holds, stop adding water. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Cold butter in food proprocessorprocessorceessor with flour and sugar" class="wp-image-47475" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1200x799.jpg" alt="Cold butter in food proprocessorprocessorceessor with flour and sugar" class="wp-image-47475" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-instructions.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47476" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47476" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<p>Turn out onto a surface and knead briefly. Shape into a disk, wrap in plastic, and refrigerate for 30 minutes.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47477" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47477" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-crumble.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47478" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47478" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-dough-disc.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-make-the-filling"><strong>Make the Filling</strong></h3>



<p>In a bowl, toss blueberries with sugar, lemon juice, and zest. Sprinkle cornstarch over top and toss again. Let sit while dough chills.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47479" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47479" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-filling.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47480" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47480" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-tossed-filling.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-assemble-the-galette"><strong>Assemble the Galette</strong></h3>



<p>Roll the chilled dough into a 12-inch circle on lightly floured parchment. Gently transfer the dough and parchment to a baking sheet before adding filling. Spoon blueberries into the center, leaving a 2-inch border. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47481" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47481" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-rolled-dough.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47482" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47482" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-assembling.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<p>Fold up the sides, pleating every few inches.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47483" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47483" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-folding-instructions.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-bake-until-golden"><strong>Bake Until Golden</strong></h3>



<p>Brush crust with egg wash and sprinkle with coarse sugar. Bake at 425°F for 26–31 minutes, or until the crust is golden brown and filling is bubbling. Let cool for 10 minutes before slicing and serving.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-ad2f72ca wp-block-group-is-layout-flex">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47485" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47485" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-20.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20799'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" class="wp-image-47486" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22.jpg 2048w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1200x799.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="799" src="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1200x799.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-47486" srcset="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1200x799.jpg 1200w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-500x333.jpg 500w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22-1536x1022.jpg 1536w, https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Blueberry-Galette-full-size-22.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-group has-lightgreen-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-expert-tips-for-success"><strong>Expert Tips for Success</strong></h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Keep ingredients cold</strong>: Use very cold butter and ice water so the dough stays flaky.</li>



<li><strong>Avoid over-processing</strong>: Pulse the dough until just combined—don’t let it turn to paste.</li>



<li><strong>Watch for soggy crust</strong>: Dry blueberries before mixing. Don’t let filling sit too long.</li>



<li><strong>Transfer before filling</strong>: Move the dough to the baking sheet before adding berries.</li>



<li><strong>Cracking? No problem</strong>: Pinch the dough back together if the edges crack while folding.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-make-ahead-storage-amp-freezing"><strong>Make Ahead, Storage &amp; Freezing</strong></h3>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Dough</strong> can be made and refrigerated for up to 2 days in advance.</li>



<li><strong>Baked galette</strong> keeps at room temp for 2 days in an airtight container.</li>



<li><strong>Freezing</strong>: Cool completely, then wrap and freeze for up to 2 months.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="schema-faq wp-block-yoast-faq-block"><div class="schema-faq-section" id="faq-question-1750801696299"><strong class="schema-faq-question">Can I use frozen blueberries?</strong> <p class="schema-faq-answer">Yes, But do not thaw them. I like to add an extra 1/2 tablespoon of cornstarch to account for extra moisture.</p> </div> <div class="schema-faq-section" id="faq-question-1750801743340"><strong class="schema-faq-question">How do I fold a galette?</strong> <p class="schema-faq-answer">roll to a 1/4 inch dough, leave a 2 inch border around your filling, pinch cracks around the edge and fold over and pleate covering your filling leaving the middle open.</p> </div> <div class="schema-faq-section" id="faq-question-1750802147344"><strong class="schema-faq-question">Can I Use other Fruits?</strong> <p class="schema-faq-answer">Absolutley! My <a href="https://www.fifteenspatulas.com/fresh-peach-crostata/">Peach Crostata</a> is great with fresh peaches</p> </div> </div>



